{"article_id":"wyLa2qnVpApNadF6","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Douglas McAuthur McCain , from the San Diego area , is reportedly the first and only American citizen","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"to die","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"waging jihad with ISIS .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"NBC News has the scoop :","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"The battle in itself seemed tragically normal .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Two Syrian opposition groups fought","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"and there were heavy casualties on both sides .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Then victorious rebels rifled through the pockets of the dead .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"One contained about $ 800 in cash","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"-- and an American passport .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Douglas McAuthur McCain , of San Diego , California , was killed over the weekend","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"fighting for the Islamic State of Iraq and al-Sham","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"( ISIS ) ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"according to the Free Syrian Army .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Photos of McCain 's passport and of his body","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"-- which feature a distinctive neck tattoo --","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"have been seen by NBC News .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"According to an activist","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"linked to the Free Syrian Army","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"who also saw the body and travel document ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"McCain was among three foreign jihadis","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"fighting with ISIS","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"who died during the battle .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Given the group ' s well-cultivated reputation as a known terrorist organization more brutal than al Qaeda ,","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"it ' s certainly jarring to read","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Western nationals , let alone American citizens , would join their ranks .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"Perhaps this is why McCain ' s own cousin has denied the rumors ,","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"claiming instead","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"he was \" a loving person \"","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"who would never \" support a terrorist group like that \" :","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Maybe not .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"But either way , he ' s dead .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"And what ' s more , his own uncle","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"( and US officials )","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"believe","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"he was a terrorist","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"( via CNN ) :","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"The man 's uncle , Ken McCain , said","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that his nephew had gone to fight as a jihadi","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"and that the U.S. State Department told the family Monday about the death .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Like U.S. officials , the group characterized McCain as an ISIS fighter","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"he was killed","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"battling al-Nusra Front , an al Qaeda-linked organization","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"that the U.S. government has blacklisted as a foreign terror organization .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"He was also writing empathetic posts on Facebook about the organization ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"according to one expert familiar with the case ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"which is why he was clearly on terrorist watch lists :","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"U.S. counterterrorism investigators had been looking into McCain 's activities for some time before his death ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"one U.S. official said .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"He was on a list of Americans","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"who are believed to have joined militant groups","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"and who would be stopped","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"and subjected to additional scrutiny","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"if he traveled ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"according to the official .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Meanwhile , McCain is almost certainly not the only American","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"defending and fighting for ISIS ,","depth":4},{"id":58,"text":"although it ' s difficult to gauge just how many actually are .","depth":3},{"id":59,"text":"As of last June , Richard Engels reported","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"that the number is estimated to be somewhere around 70 :","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"Americans in # isis .","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"US officials say","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"about seventy US fighters have passed through Syria","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"and about a dozen are currently active there .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"- Richard Engel","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"( @ RichardEngel )","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"June 30 , 2014","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"But more recently , the US State Department believes","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"maybe more Americans have openly declared war against the stars and stripes :","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"`` Dozens of Americans , perhaps up to 100 , '' are among those","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"who have tried to join various militant groups there ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"State Department spokeswoman Marie Harf told CNN .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"Needless to say ,","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"these defectors speak English ,","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"possess US passports ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"and have deep ties to the country .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":153,"left":132,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":80,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":79,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":0,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":101,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":98,"right":100,"relation":"evaluation","nu